ol.li: Atomic Guard: Mutex must be held for all buffer_used checks.
Deadlock Avoidance: Never call schedule() or wait_event while holding dev_mutex.
Signal Awareness: TASK_INTERRUPTIBLE allows clean exits via Ctrl+C.
